{"tid":1908910,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真心支國爆好撚開心 但殺到去日歐了 心情灰灰地","createTime":"2020-03-03T15:06:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T13:43:32.000Z","uid":281784,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"63b2173cf11c7eb9f30e55ccb1633f53f3422c6b","tid":1908910,"uid":281784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T15:06:33.000Z","msg":"由一月開始 睇撚住支國 日日二千咁爆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係爽撚過打飛機 射到我軟撚曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n心諗終於等到支爆 支國人終於有報應<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日日 好似期指咁 爆升 心情不知幾撚興奮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但上兩個星期開始 直線下滑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲搞撚到 日本 韓國 歐洲 開始仆街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n美帝估計 同樣下場 真心灰機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁點算好 希望美帝頂撚住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4484d57b5931f7e392a36146d54d7a3b306b8b9","tid":1908910,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T15:08:54.000Z","msg":"強国人命賤<br />\n<br />\n有病掘個窿埋鳩左佢成本低廉<br />\n<br />\n美帝人命貴<br />\n<br />\n醫條友都過百萬<br />\n<br />\n邊個傷？"},{"pid":"dcdd62993c403029b58fb0e075f31c1adbed2f1e","tid":1908910,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T15:36:38.000Z","msg":"襯機會推到全球反支啦<br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n（國際戰線）借助日韓爆發武肺推動全球反奶共運動和全球排支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1894747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a8a4f4db74c361cbe626a2fe881806c1612f35ca","tid":1908910,"uid":281784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4484d57b5931f7e392a36146d54d7a3b306b8b9","tid":1908910,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T15:08:54.000Z","msg":"強国人命賤<br />\n<br />\n有病掘個窿埋鳩左佢成本低廉<br />\n<br />\n美帝人命貴<br />\n<br />\n醫條友都過百萬<br />\n<br />\n邊個傷？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T15:45:28.000Z","msg":"希望美帝無事 唔係到時 支國人 又自我感覺良好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3987266eb89885fbe468d9974c97ab174a17fcf3","tid":1908910,"uid":281784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T13:43:32.000Z","msg":"爆埋美帝真心gg"}]}